
Prerequisites

1. Make sure both scripts have permissions to be executed
2. Make sure your package manager has permissions to install third-party packages
3. Make sure to run scripts using sudo
4. Installer script is expecting apt to be available. If it's not an option
you can install the .deb packages yourself or modify the script accordingly.

Installation

1. Run Installer.sh It will take care of itself and
install the game to /usr/local/bin/Tower

you can go there yourself or use Runner.sh
to run the game
